{"h196909e3g39a2g4127g9474gea6de4c7a880": ["It's quite a sight.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "e4406ff8-e8ee-4a3c-c3bc-3ac36f8cb7dc"], "h7841da51ga54cg4d1aga449gcec784ac1d79": ["The stars, I mean. I could take or leave your chin.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "5833377f-38ab-c4de-d2d1-a4fea035c106"], "heca82d0bg0569g48a1g96a3gefb9b616b9d9": ["They are beautiful tonight.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "f731ea76-1594-500b-8777-13cdf4bd1d6e"], "h4373ee91g4b1bg44cbg861eg967607d24dcc": ["I can see the stars from Baldur's Gate, of course, but not with such clarity. It got me thinking.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "80b149f3-d22e-4fa5-f658-142de4f62ded"], "h521ae609g5caag4804gbe6fg9dda9d04c5c1": ["Reflecting on what tomorrow might bring, when we find the druid.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "ba87f762-7ea7-5dc6-cb3d-f7cda436d229"], "h6dbe07a8gfda2g4b22g8cbcg6c6254cc61d7": ["Will he know how to bring the worm under control? Will this little adventure of ours be over?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "8d0b489e-eb1e-ddb3-5e04-024cd86424e0"], "hb3963566gd772g4845gbc31g456d1b7b8de9": ["It doesn't have to be. We can still travel together.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "60a29c5b-fc4f-a75d-466d-620e643ec897"], "h18d48f04gc476g444cgb858geb531af5dd11": ["Good! I don't want you to run off just yet.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "ec51be6b-2a8a-b65a-b35c-b64074f75d6c"], "ha2cab3fegf561g4057g9e56g74a155370319": ["You're quite the ally, after all. Traversing Avernus. Surviving the crash. Surviving everything that's followed...", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "b8a6d69f-799a-eb66-46d2-71a5efea6fc6"], "hd9320845g6708g4992gafdeg08c79b6ae21c": ["I'm not normally impressed by people of your stature, but you're stronger than I gave you credit for.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "ad7b7b86-b2ee-0c8c-54e8-2d6abcc82fa1"], "h7b20a1c3g0194g4d5dgba4bgd302bb77e046": ["I'm not easily impressed by people, but you're stronger than I gave you credit for.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "ad7b7b86-b2ee-0c8c-54e8-2d6abcc82fa1"], "h01e19659g5e08g49a4ga412g57504f28ec15": ["True. I am pretty impressive.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "93d78fdb-b2bd-0d7d-a675-0f2c4a666231"], "hc9ab3c4fg30eag4b62g9f07g28386871c701": ["Aren't you just...", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "62e9f674-f997-89f0-f19f-8b79528841cc"], "ha2cf106dg9895g43a1gb791g56d4103889bf": ["Are you feeling all right?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "a71186ee-c7c1-0218-467c-fd9a97137c0d"], "hbe0bbd97g68bcg4ef4g912ag21246fffd520": ["Hmm? Oh, I was leagues away. I just need to...", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "eee222b1-91e2-22dd-f8a1-1c592415a718"], "h1923c6a2g19e2g413cg8a4bg18daf7cefacb": ["...get some air. Clear my head.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "31eb455d-bbf8-88bf-b1b8-7e2a59a5cc95"], "h8a40ffd7g5c62g4e79gaa23gae6521e562c6": ["I'll see you later, I'm sure. Sleep tight.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "e62e0523-e40a-f89b-6a81-371cecca1ff8"], "ha10e1e9cg2002g4ac9g81e2g729a86a1a802": ["You can stop staring.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "5d12fdbf-87a2-8b68-ae11-b48a99a777b9"], "h994663b3g0dedg4c3eg884bgb5bc7492c3d5": ["Was I? I just...", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "7144892f-57ff-b55d-e34f-d342e5b1e3bf"], "hedbd3402g5770g4b95g984fgec0b8d6ecf24": ["...I just need to get some air. Clear my head.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "a241013c-ac12-8db9-db39-c3395b034872"], "he5b5e23fg94e5g4f5bga286g60e7fa868b07": ["Just don't try to bite me again. It won't go well for you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "7d9a8b18-bdc5-f01a-6730-b7f62eaabfa4"], "hd6a637a2g8cfdg4f35g8ef0g309d259d82b9": ["Heavens forbid. I've learned my lesson. I just...", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "737ea01a-ccc4-5435-0bab-ca33aa7146c7"], "h4aefaf1cge8e1g4c6ag9408g6196ce8baf3c": ["<i>Turn and walk away.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "90061004-7987-9f9e-8e82-ea4ea0f7b3b6"], "h201db3a9g9d93g4ddag848fg373e8c2f466b": ["Sleep tight. I'll see you later, I'm sure.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "7753729b-be7f-615b-56ec-5a9720a76b3b"], "hfd99308cg2b58g455dg884bga7e03e50492e": ["I'm just trying to survive. Like you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "4c787fd2-95e6-5510-449e-c63c5e545e25"], "hc78d2f8fg4350g4687g87ffg125911ca24c2": ["Yes, we're more similar than I thought...", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "5c918a40-eb2b-9fa9-2733-b1b1fff6226d"], "h9ca5726fgffedg48aeg8cc7g7792fdb1af36": ["I have many talents. If you want to explore them...", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "358dc779-2410-3552-3ed8-8dc34c047df7"], "ha4a6bfccg362eg4507g9f6fg81cf7488ddae": ["A delicious thought, but...", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "30400812-c4de-edb8-58ac-55ffa8936793"], "hbb523b3bgbd5ag4358gbce8g9e734e6e80a4": ["But? What are you waiting for?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "d3aee2a4-15e6-9e74-b650-63fe18a0c7d7"], "h4690e73eg3cceg4d99ga477gbb5550d2335c": ["The right moment...", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "979d7ca9-2536-14f5-1981-74fb4ec05f85"], "hd9c4af83geabag49a5g972fgc94b143c2114": ["... I'm sorry, I - I need to clear my head.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "6966c22e-9996-ca2d-bdf7-6cd9ab0e80d0"], "h6b4f2019gdcb9g4124gbe05g69ff854a8c1f": ["I'm joking. Relax.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "af3808f8-b0ef-32c4-01ef-d3862727a709"], "h68293468gf94eg412egabbag546af2d6c22a": ["Hmm? Yes! Of course, me too.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "db08238e-43d0-a0ef-8139-b713bf3b9c70"], "h08114721gf321g45b4g9987g4b4e2b49f3a4": ["I think I'll just - just clear my head.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "c1345d20-7701-2e43-a75d-1a984d7479f6"], "hced8bd00gb348g4b16gb27fg776bfd664f52": ["Just keep your eyes away from my neck.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "ce1435fd-cd56-cf8c-3a86-a7b74c7d3c26"], "hddd63342gb486g4fa9gb0c0g483403041625": ["<i>A waste of time. Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "c758dace-f250-7c94-2895-1d13fc9176e7"], "hed5377a5g674dg4a42gb201g7259f5264393": ["You're too close.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "4f3fecbc-17b9-9fb0-f682-b2a801d8853c"], "hf0cec608gecc8g4878g9ea5g963e40e7a4cf": ["Of course. Terribly sorry.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "9062d6b9-32dd-4c4f-7e59-5e72b1a167f7"], "hf7db7e8dgc508g406dga5acg1d613660b76a": ["I was just going anyway. I need to clear my head.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "95505f24-efab-c155-7dca-a7e08f647a6d"], "hae91c32cgba7ag46f9gbf33g1ca092023142": ["I'm sure I'll see you when I get back. Sleep tight.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "4a88fd97-67bf-ed75-6788-261a75bc7700"], "h4c3677b5g696dg4c86gb4e9ge0f1231c1b2f": ["Probably. Once the worm is gone, I'm going my own way.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "2886afb2-eb32-6360-ec41-94d1d7f62761"], "h179926c9gab08g4c25ga459g8047883d62df": ["A pity. A great pity.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "ce6814bf-a609-a005-e92d-5dc3fc1827fd"], "h2c99dbccg1d42g4c2bg9a9dg1e769c0250b8": ["What? Will you miss me?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "f4cb6662-794e-796e-03cd-466ebafeee96"], "hbdd11658g2a16g42a9ga97fge7ae28ecf207": ["Ha! Why not?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "3feaac86-8660-5b8a-dd0b-4dc923ab7ed8"], "hefbfc7f9g134eg4958g9cf8g3d2dcf2f9648": ["You've been to the Hells and back. Survived the crash. Survived everything that's followed.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "31e2d918-e782-6d7c-fad7-d8d32e33e1de"], "hfb1b74b9g3b3ag4e75g9870g2ba0f02aa083": ["Reflecting on what tomorrow might bring, when we meet this goblin priestess.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "217dd88f-de3a-266d-3356-d9225b651a78"], "hc769bf9fg810dg4913gaef6g65a4da7e5b6c": ["Will she know how to bring the worm under control? Will this little adventure of ours be over?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "0d6c588a-b992-ae43-8d48-f08d9e260a5a"], "hd43c97aagbf3fg4fbag9479g56b50844c936": ["Reflecting on what tomorrow might bring, when we arrive at this gith cr\u00e8che.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "9d8fdaa3-9d2a-2fa8-9b3c-dd07cc0aa4bd"], "h85a390a8g4ebeg4f04gafbfgff65e90dad58": ["Will we find out how to bring the worm under control? Will this little adventure of ours be over?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "782c5817-0429-336d-087f-c55e3d482d29"], "h82c9dc3eg9425g4e99g92b9gb8a2fbe63e91": ["Reflecting on what tomorrow might bring, when we get to this hag's teahouse.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "91a016ed-cddc-0da6-822b-5112b1fbd9d9"], "h33d273a5g25c3g4845g9c38gb11b127c3eb2": ["Reflecting on what tomorrow might bring.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "cffaf010-2b9e-9d94-754d-80ba39cef765"], "h75c3d29cg7686g4d94gaf4bgdb4488366360": ["Am I disturbing you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "c61be45d-6fcf-d668-998b-f0188b0e60f8"], "h03313f8dgf947g44aag9d5bg4d7dffa3efc4": ["No, just thinking.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "6e27e53f-fc5e-3e77-b72d-5c35529b4823"], "h09cf96b7g3091g4292g9355g85347e55e2b4": ["You seem more relaxed.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "75289c6c-fbb1-cb10-8400-6f11e8354cb7"], "h66456786g1fd1g44bfg91e2geb98276699d1": ["I am. I've been thinking.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "708cdfc0-6544-3fcf-49be-103acd5608e8"], "he90c4c3dga1f0g4426g8114g7e7ca59e4b66": ["You know, I've been thinking.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_Night3_CRD_Astarion.html", "eb2cdff0-e7be-8a3d-5f33-bb12550e78ac"]}